{"tid":731224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持《薩爾達傳說》大師之劍攻擊室友　美男大生被捕","createTime":"2018-07-06T04:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T07:48:46.000Z","uid":1735,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c300c2e4f4f3ac706d0f242b849b1d1f136471a6","tid":731224,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"為什麼隨手拿起的武器會是「大師之劍」啊！？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/123937_467caf4070e749256f68588ded599b34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F123937_467caf4070e749256f68588ded599b34.png&h=66dc6548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國阿拉斯加州一名22歲男性持《薩爾達傳說》遊戲內登場的「大師之劍」複製品攻擊室友。<br />\n<br />\n根據阿拉斯加州地方媒體 Anchorage Daily News 報導，當地警察在1月26日凌晨零時30分左右接獲通報，嫌犯Jeremy Tazruk在阿拉斯加大學安克拉治校區附近的宿舍內，與其他室友發生衝突，現場發現損壞的電視與沾血的桌巾、餐桌刀以及一把「彎曲的劍」。<br />\n<br />\n據嫌犯Tazruk與其他證人的說法，原先是一位名叫「T.P.」的學生將其中一位室友壓制，隨後其他室友也紛紛加入戰局，Tazruk遂拿起倚在牆壁旁的《薩爾達傳說》「大師之劍」複製品，並用刀鞘端毆打「T.P.」數回。法院提出的書面資料表示：「劍刃並不銳利，但刀尖還蠻銳的」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Tazruk因為使用菜刀等器具攻擊「T.P.」兩次，以「第4級傷害罪」及「危害他人安全罪」遭到逮捕，「T.P.」則因肋骨遭到刺傷，被送到醫療中心診治。"},{"pid":"debdd88dd38d74fdc1c2b1c538a915ecdc833c30","tid":731224,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"又話唔扣耐久度"},{"pid":"6a28a4bbf0e8daa017667dc63bb3ae3354d43385","tid":731224,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f06a9ebb75fd60aabe262e30e2dea936e334ef6","tid":731224,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"debdd88dd38d74fdc1c2b1c538a915ecdc833c30","tid":731224,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"又話唔扣耐久度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"要時間recharge嘛"},{"pid":"2611ddc90d1433ba37046fb48a7d7a0690f5af93","tid":731224,"uid":115801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"幸好Tazruk當時唔係滿血，如果唔係出劍氣實攪出人命。"},{"pid":"faf7082283587ef1ce47717da9a1a99de0600763","tid":731224,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834d02d3913f19b1215f4cd793056d82efb88e87","tid":731224,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"登~登登登登登登~登登登登登登"}]}